caption.p:
Heatmap showing the relative frequency of each group of compounds is presented for each of the most common 
   Citrus species. Data represent the number of compounds reported in each category divided by the total number of compounds reported in each particular species, according to the scale below: 
   red, high frequency; 
   black, intermediate frequency; 
   green, low frequency. The qualitative data used is available in 
   Supplementary Table S5.
